# mojibake-allowlist — paths where U+FFFD detection is suppressed.
#
# One glob per line. Patterns are matched against the file path both
# relative to the repo root and absolute. Shell glob syntax applies
# (* and ?); ** is treated as *. Blank lines and # comments are ignored.
#
# Default entries protect the hook source itself and test fixtures from
# self-detection loops. Add project-specific paths here if a file
# legitimately contains U+FFFD (e.g. documentation about the issue).

.claude/hooks/check_mojibake.sh
tests/fixtures/**
docs/plans/**/2026-04-17-mojibake-postedit-guard.md
docs/plans/**/*mojibake*.md
docs/reports/**/*mojibake*.md
